This isn't your average read me as this is really a private project for just one site.  In the future, I'll make this into something other people can use to set this site up with their own hosting.  For now just notice that there are some initializers you'll need to configure for your specific instance.

Forums
  splitting a single post into multiple posts
  silent edits
  mark post as unread for self
  showing posts as unread after being edited
Guides
  each guide should have a forum thread
Loots
  search by slot
  search by type